{"title":"从零搭建 AI 助手的记忆系统","uid":"9626534725b22ae206460e868953b6fb","slug":"从零搭建AI助手的记忆系统","date":"2026-04-17T15:40:00.000Z","updated":"2026-04-17T15:50:10.507Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/从零搭建AI助手的记忆系统.json","keywords":"记录, 学习, ClaRnS","cover":"/gallery/ml.png","content":"<p>在构建 AI 助手时，我们往往专注于对话能力和工具调用，却忽略了一个关键问题：<strong>记忆</strong>。没有记忆的 AI 就像金鱼，每次对话都是全新的开始。本文将手把手教你搭建一套生产级的 AI 记忆系统。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n\n<h2 id=\"一、为什么-AI-助手需要记忆？\"><a href=\"#一、为什么-AI-助手需要记忆？\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一、为什么 AI 助手需要记忆？\"></a>一、为什么 AI 助手需要记忆？</h2><h3 id=\"短期记忆的局限\"><a href=\"#短期记忆的局限\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"短期记忆的局限\"></a>短期记忆的局限</h3><p>当前的大语言模型都受限于<strong>上下文窗口</strong>。虽然 GPT-4 已经支持 128k token，但：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>长对话会挤占思考空间</li>\n<li>超出窗口后早期信息会被遗忘</li>\n<li>每次重启对话，上下文清零</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"长期记忆的价值\"><a href=\"#长期记忆的价值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"长期记忆的价值\"></a>长期记忆的价值</h3><p>真正的智能助手应该记住：</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>用户背景</strong>：姓名、职业、偏好、习惯</li>\n<li><strong>历史决策</strong>：之前做过的选择和原因</li>\n<li><strong>技术方案</strong>：讨论过的架构和配置</li>\n<li><strong>待办事项</strong>：未完成的任务和截止日期</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"记忆的分类\"><a href=\"#记忆的分类\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"记忆的分类\"></a>记忆的分类</h3><p>在 memory-lancedb-pro 中，记忆被分为四类：</p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>类型</th>\n<th>说明</th>\n<th>示例</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td><strong>fact</strong></td>\n<td>客观事实</td>\n<td>用户是计算机专业学生，2025年毕业</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>decision</strong></td>\n<td>决策记录</td>\n<td>选择 LanceDB 而非 Pinecone</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>reflection</strong></td>\n<td>经验反思</td>\n<td>配置 embedding 模型时要注意 API key</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>entity</strong></td>\n<td>实体信息</td>\n<td>项目名称、技术栈版本</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"二、技术选型：LanceDB\"><a href=\"#二、技术选型：LanceDB\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二、技术选型：LanceDB\"></a>二、技术选型：LanceDB</h2><h3 id=\"什么是-LanceDB\"><a href=\"#什么是-LanceDB\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"什么是 LanceDB\"></a>什么是 LanceDB</h3><p><a href=\"https://lancedb.github.io/lancedb/\">LanceDB</a> 是一个<strong>云原生向量数据库</strong>，专为 AI 应用设计：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>基于 Apache Arrow 和 Lance 格式</li>\n<li>支持向量搜索 + 全文搜索 + SQL</li>\n<li>零配置、无服务器部署</li>\n<li>Python&#x2F;JS&#x2F;Rust 多语言 SDK</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"为什么选择-LanceDB\"><a href=\"#为什么选择-LanceDB\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"为什么选择 LanceDB\"></a>为什么选择 LanceDB</h3><p><strong>性能优势：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>比 Pinecone 快 10 倍的向量检索</li>\n<li>磁盘存储成本低，无需全部加载到内存</li>\n<li>原生支持多模态数据（文本、图像、向量）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>生态优势：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>OpenClaw 官方唯一支持的 memory 插件</li>\n<li>与 OpenClaw 深度集成，配置简单</li>\n<li>活跃的社区和持续的更新</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"与其他方案对比\"><a href=\"#与其他方案对比\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"与其他方案对比\"></a>与其他方案对比</h3><table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>特性</th>\n<th>LanceDB</th>\n<th>Pinecone</th>\n<th>Milvus</th>\n<th>Chroma</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody><tr>\n<td>部署方式</td>\n<td>嵌入式&#x2F;云服务</td>\n<td>纯云服务</td>\n<td>自托管&#x2F;云</td>\n<td>嵌入式</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>存储成本</td>\n<td>低（磁盘）</td>\n<td>高（内存）</td>\n<td>中</td>\n<td>低</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>向量维度</td>\n<td>无限制</td>\n<td>2048</td>\n<td>32768</td>\n<td>无限制</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>混合搜索</td>\n<td>✅</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>✅</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>OpenClaw支持</td>\n<td>✅官方</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n<td>❌</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h2 id=\"三、环境准备与安装\"><a href=\"#三、环境准备与安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"三、环境准备与安装\"></a>三、环境准备与安装</h2><h3 id=\"系统要求\"><a href=\"#系统要求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"系统要求\"></a>系统要求</h3><ul>\n<li>Python 3.8+</li>\n<li>2GB+ 内存（根据数据量调整）</li>\n<li>磁盘空间 10GB+</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装-memory-lancedb-pro\"><a href=\"#安装-memory-lancedb-pro\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装 memory-lancedb-pro\"></a>安装 memory-lancedb-pro</h3><div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 克隆插件到 OpenClaw skills 目录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">git</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">clone</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">https://github.com/openclaw/memory-lancedb-pro.git</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 安装依赖</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">cd</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">memory-lancedb-pro</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">pip</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">install</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-r</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">requirements.txt</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"配置-OpenClaw\"><a href=\"#配置-OpenClaw\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"配置 OpenClaw\"></a>配置 OpenClaw</h3><p>编辑 <code>~/.openclaw/openclaw.json</code>：</p>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">plugins</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">memory</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">      </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">provider</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">lancedb-pro</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">      </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">config</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">db_path</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">embedding_model</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">BAAI/bge-m3</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">embedding_api_key</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">your-api-key</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">rerank_enabled</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">true</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">smart_extraction</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">          </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">enabled</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">true</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">          </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">llm_provider</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">openrouter</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">          </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">llm_model</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">openai/gpt-oss-120b:free</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">        </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">      </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"四、核心配置详解\"><a href=\"#四、核心配置详解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"四、核心配置详解\"></a>四、核心配置详解</h2><h3 id=\"Embedding-模型选择\"><a href=\"#Embedding-模型选择\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Embedding 模型选择\"></a>Embedding 模型选择</h3><p><strong>推荐：BAAI&#x2F;bge-m3</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>多语言支持（中英日韩等）</li>\n<li>8192 token 长文本</li>\n<li>免费使用（通过 SiliconFlow）</li>\n<li>在 MTEB 榜单上表现优异</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">embedding_model</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">BAAI/bge-m3</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">embedding_api_key</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">sk-your-siliconflow-key</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">embedding_base_url</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">https://api.siliconflow.cn/v1</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"Rerank-配置\"><a href=\"#Rerank-配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Rerank 配置\"></a>Rerank 配置</h3><p>Rerank 可以显著提升检索质量：</p>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">rerank_enabled</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">true</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">rerank_model</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>作用：</strong> 先向量召回 Top-K，再用 rerank 模型精排，最后取 Top-N。</p>\n<h3 id=\"Smart-Extraction-设置\"><a href=\"#Smart-Extraction-设置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Smart Extraction 设置\"></a>Smart Extraction 设置</h3><p>Smart Extraction 自动从对话中提取关键信息：</p>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">smart_extraction</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">enabled</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">true</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">llm_provider</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">openrouter</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">llm_model</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">openai/gpt-oss-120b:free</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">api_key</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">sk-or-your-openrouter-key</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>提取策略：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>每轮对话后自动分析</li>\n<li>识别重要信息（事实、决策、待办）</li>\n<li>生成简洁的记忆文本</li>\n<li>自动分类（fact&#x2F;decision&#x2F;reflection&#x2F;entity）</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"多-Scope-隔离\"><a href=\"#多-Scope-隔离\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"多 Scope 隔离\"></a>多 Scope 隔离</h3><p>支持按会话、用户、项目隔离记忆：</p>\n<div class=\"language-python\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">python</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 存储时指定 scope</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">memory_store</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">(</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">text</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">用户是计算机专业学生</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">scope</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">user:example_user</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">category</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">fact</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 检索时限定 scope</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">memory_recall</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">(</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">query</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">用户背景</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">scope</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">user:example_user</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">)</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"五、踩坑记录\"><a href=\"#五、踩坑记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"五、踩坑记录\"></a>五、踩坑记录</h2><h3 id=\"坑-1：403-错误-模型配置问题\"><a href=\"#坑-1：403-错误-模型配置问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 1：403 错误 - 模型配置问题\"></a>坑 1：403 错误 - 模型配置问题</h3><p><strong>现象：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"language-txt\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">txt</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #dbd7caee\">Error: 403 Forbidden - model unknown</span></span></code></pre></div><p><strong>原因：</strong> embedding 模型字段被错误设置</p>\n<p><strong>解决：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">embedding_model</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">BAAI/bge-m3</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #758575DD\">// 不要写成 &quot;unknown&quot; 或其他无效值</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"坑-2：超时问题\"><a href=\"#坑-2：超时问题\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 2：超时问题\"></a>坑 2：超时问题</h3><p><strong>现象：</strong> 大量记忆检索时超时</p>\n<p><strong>解决：</strong> 增加超时配置</p>\n<div class=\"language-json\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">json</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">timeout_ms</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">30000</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">connection_timeout_ms</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">10000</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"坑-3：API-Key-过期\"><a href=\"#坑-3：API-Key-过期\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 3：API Key 过期\"></a>坑 3：API Key 过期</h3><p><strong>现象：</strong> 突然无法存储&#x2F;检索记忆</p>\n<p><strong>解决：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>检查 <code>embedding_api_key</code> 是否过期</li>\n<li>更新 SiliconFlow&#x2F;OpenRouter 的 key</li>\n<li>重启 OpenClaw Gateway</li>\n</ol>\n<h3 id=\"坑-4：磁盘空间不足\"><a href=\"#坑-4：磁盘空间不足\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"坑 4：磁盘空间不足\"></a>坑 4：磁盘空间不足</h3><p><strong>现象：</strong> LanceDB 写入失败</p>\n<p><strong>解决：</strong></p>\n<div class=\"language-bash\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">bash</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 清理旧记忆</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #80A665\">rm</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C99076\">-rf</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">~/.openclaw/memory/lancedb/old_collections</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 或者配置自动清理</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">&quot;auto_cleanup&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">&quot;enabled&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4D9375\">true</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">&quot;max_age_days&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">90</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #80A665\">&quot;min_importance&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #B8A965\">:</span><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\"> </span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">0.5</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">  </span><span style=\"color: #666666\">&#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"六、实际应用场景\"><a href=\"#六、实际应用场景\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"六、实际应用场景\"></a>六、实际应用场景</h2><h3 id=\"场景-1：用户背景记忆\"><a href=\"#场景-1：用户背景记忆\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"场景 1：用户背景记忆\"></a>场景 1：用户背景记忆</h3><div class=\"language-python\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">python</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 首次对话时记录</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">memory_store</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">(</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">text</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">用户是计算机专业学生，2025年毕业，将从事软件开发工作</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">category</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">fact</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">importance</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">0.9</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 后续对话自动检索</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 用户：&quot;帮我看看这个简历&quot;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 系统自动 recall：用户是计算机专业、找开发工作...</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"场景-2：技术方案记录\"><a href=\"#场景-2：技术方案记录\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"场景 2：技术方案记录\"></a>场景 2：技术方案记录</h3><div class=\"language-python\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">python</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 记录技术决策</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">memory_store</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">(</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">text</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">选择 LanceDB 作为向量数据库，原因是：OpenClaw官方支持、性能好、免费</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">category</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">decision</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">importance</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">0.8</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 后续相关问题时自动提供上下文</span></span></code></pre></div><h3 id=\"场景-3：待办事项追踪\"><a href=\"#场景-3：待办事项追踪\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"场景 3：待办事项追踪\"></a>场景 3：待办事项追踪</h3><div class=\"language-python\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">python</span><pre class=\"shiki vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># 记录待办</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">memory_store</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">(</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">text</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">待办：配置 AnythingLLM 与 OpenClaw 联动</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">category</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D\">reflection</span><span style=\"color: #C98A7D99\">&quot;</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">,</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #DBD7CAEE\">    </span><span style=\"color: #BD976A\">importance</span><span style=\"color: #666666\">=</span><span style=\"color: #4C9A91\">0.7</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #666666\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #758575DD\"># Heartbeat 任务中检查并提醒</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"七、总结\"><a href=\"#七、总结\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"七、总结\"></a>七、总结</h2><p>通过 LanceDB 和 memory-lancedb-pro，我们可以为 AI 助手构建一套<strong>生产级的长期记忆系统</strong>：</p>\n<p><strong>核心优势：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ 跨会话记忆持久化</li>\n<li>✅ 智能信息提取（Smart Extraction）</li>\n<li>✅ 混合检索（向量 + 关键词 + Rerank）</li>\n<li>✅ 多维度隔离（scope&#x2F;category&#x2F;importance）</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>最佳实践：</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>使用 BAAI&#x2F;bge-m3 作为 embedding 模型</li>\n<li>开启 Rerank 提升检索质量</li>\n<li>合理设置 importance 和 category</li>\n<li>定期清理低价值记忆</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>下一步：</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>结合 AnythingLLM 构建知识库</li>\n<li>使用 cron 任务定期整理记忆</li>\n<li>探索记忆的遗忘与强化机制</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p><em>本文基于实际部署经验撰写，如有问题欢迎在评论区留言交流。</em></p>\n","feature":true,"text":"在构建 AI 助手时，我们往往专注于对话能力和工具调用，却忽略了一个关键问题：记忆。没有记忆的 AI 就像金鱼，每次对话都是全新的开始。本文将手把手教你搭建一套...","permalink":"/post/从零搭建AI助手的记忆系统","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.8k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"技术分享","slug":"技术分享","count":2,"path":"api/categories/技术分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"LanceDB","slug":"LanceDB","count":1,"path":"api/tags/LanceDB.json"},{"name":"长期记忆","slug":"长期记忆","count":1,"path":"api/tags/长期记忆.json"},{"name":"向量数据库","slug":"向量数据库","count":1,"path":"api/tags/向量数据库.json"},{"name":"OpenClaw","slug":"OpenClaw","count":1,"path"